See EventAlertConfig or TaskAlertConfig for the different alert metric types in each case. For the *RATE metrics, one or both of these fields may be set. Zero is the default value and can be left at that. For *PERCENTILE_DURATION metrics, one or both of these fields may be set, and also, the duration threshold value should be specified in the threshold_duration_ms member below.
